OL,3,CJury in Ian Watkins murder trial
OL,4,Cdischarged for 'legal reasons'
OL,6,FThe jury in the trial of two serving
OL,7,Fprisoners accused of murdering
OL,8,Fpaedophile Lostprophets frontman Ian
OL,9,FWatkins has been discharged for legal
OL,10,Freasons.
OL,12,FThe disgraced singer was stabbed to
OL,13,Fdeath by 25-year-old Rico Gedel in his
OL,14,Fcell at high-security HMP Wakefield,
OL,15,Fwhere he was serving a 29-year
OL,16,Fsentence for child sexual offences.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
