OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1779719227
OL,3,CJury in Ian Watkins murder trial
OL,4,Cdischarged for 'legal reasons'
OL,6,FHe said Gedel handed the knife to him
OL,7,Fafter emerging from Watkins' cell, and
OL,8,Fhe tried to give it back but ended up
OL,9,Fthrowing it away after panicking at
OL,10,Fthe sight of an injured Watkins.
OL,12,FWatkins, of Pontypridd, was jailed for
OL,13,F29 years in December 2013, with a
OL,14,Ffurther six years on licence, after
OL,15,Fadmitting a string of sex offences,
OL,16,Fincluding the attempted rape of a
OL,17,Ffan's baby.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/6
